dct_title_s: County and municipality map of New Jersey: political boundaries as of June 1, 1924
dct_description_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Development. Division of Geology and Waters. Atlas Sheet no. 39 (1925) (County/municipality) New Jersey Geological Survey. Political boundaries as of June 1, 1924. In upper margin: Atlas sheet no. 39. Surveyed 1877-1887. Base compiled and engraved 1910-1912.
